{"tid":1670365,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊偉雄 : 智慧燈柱不會侵犯私隱   資料不會辨認到個人身份","createTime":"2019-10-23T03:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T03:56:39.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2a743eafd14dc695bcc1c86f6d4d3660873ad0e6","tid":1670365,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/10/23/2282246_6bba165427379839a228527b551acccb_320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F10%2F23%2F2282246_6bba165427379839a228527b551acccb_320.jpg&h=322d565f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n創新及科技局局長楊偉雄出席電台節目時，被問到政府有無考慮動用《緊急法》「封網」。他表示，是否「封網」是要很審慎處理的事，香港作為互聯網樞紐，要很小心處理有關政策。<br />\n<br />\n楊偉雄稱，政府早前已經表明無計劃再動用《緊急法》，強調香港資訊自由流通是核心價值，數據流量在亞太區數一數二，所有影響資訊自由流動的事情都非常嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n對於九龍灣的智慧燈柱早前被黑衣人破壞，楊偉雄表示，要增強市民對智慧燈柱的信心，一定要靠多解釋，找第三者專家檢視有無足夠保護私隱，強調要開誠布公。他指出，要讓市民看到，智慧燈柱蒐集的數據不會侵犯私隱，資料不會辨認到個人身份，例如智慧燈柱偵側到路面塞車，有多架的士在路上，但蒐集的資料不會包括的士車牌，亦不會保留。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2282246/%E6%A5%8A%E5%81%89%E9%9B%84%3A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%98%AF%E4%BA%92%E8%81%AF%E7%B6%B2%E6%A8%9E%E7%B4%90+%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%B0%81%E7%B6%B2%E9%A0%88%E5%AF%A9%E6%85%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2282246%2F%25E6%25A5%258A%25E5%2581%2589%25E9%259B%2584%253A%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2598%25AF%25E4%25BA%2592%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25A8%259E%25E7%25B4%2590%2B%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2590%25A6%25E5%25B0%2581%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E9%25A0%2588%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%2585%258E&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2Bltv2u4%2BaHFFj7NdFJeB1nj9U%3D&h=e246c0b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2282246/%E6%A5%8A%E5%81%89%E9%9B%84%3A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%98%AF%E4%BA%92%E8%81%AF%E7%B6%B2%E6%A8%9E%E7%B4%90+%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%B0%81%E7%B6%B2%E9%A0%88%E5%AF%A9%E6%85%8E</a>"},{"pid":"52426db26fed2b1270b82aa84c376a459006fccf","tid":1670365,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:30:40.000Z","msg":"但係我唔想俾你地監視"},{"pid":"67ab28e7e2603b2aebcef60f4bd49c83545404ee","tid":1670365,"uid":23162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:31:00.000Z","msg":"有毒氣體對人體無害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91623c13893d372e0e5fb386ca60ad35d3b37123","tid":1670365,"uid":256142,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:32:55.000Z","msg":"楊偉雄 : 眼同腦唔相連<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a4c2f3c9a55f0dab34cfc020fd156a509f4cb5","tid":1670365,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:35:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">一、誠意推薦：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃</em></strong><br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2Bltv2u4%2BaHFFj7NdFJeB1nj9U%3D&h=9107748d\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2Bltv2u4%2BaHFFj7NdFJeB1nj9